<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3632630>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Habitat photos of Hemiphyllodactylus nilgiriensis sp. nov. near Mulli view point, Kilkunda, The Nilgiris District, Tamil Nadu, India (top panel) and Hemiphyllodactylus peninsularis sp. nov. near Sengaltheri, Kalakad Mundanthurai Tiger Reserve, Tirunelveli District, Tamil Nadu, India (lower panel)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3632630/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3632624>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Hemiphyllodactylus nilgiriensis sp. nov. (holotype, BNHS 2632): (A) dorsal view of body, (B) ventral view of body, (C) type series of Hemiphyllodactylus nilgiriensis sp. nov. Scale bars 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3632624/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3632626>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Hemiphyllodactylus nilgiriensis sp. nov. (holotype, BNHS 2632): (A) dorsal view of head, (B) ventral view of head, (C) lateral view of head, (D) view of cloacal region showing precloacal and femoral pores. Scale bars 4 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3632626/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3632628>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Hemiphyllodactylus nilgiriensis sp. nov. in life: (A) male holotype, BNHS 2632, (B) female paratype, CESL 467, (C) male paratype BNHS 2437 dorsal view, (D) male paratype BNHS 2437 ventral view, (E) male paratype BNHS 2436 dorsal view, (F) male paratype BNHS 2436 ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3632628/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

